<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00">其實，<delay8 />我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />借了個東西，
但一直都沒拿去還<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉，<delay8 />我怎麼這麼迷糊啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在我實在是<delay8 />
沒臉<delay8 />拿去還<gender3 m="他" f="她" />。<delay20 />
唉～<delay8 />這該怎麼辦啊<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我幫你還吧？</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實地道歉吧</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />來我家玩，<delay8 />
結果<gender3 m="他" f="她" />把東西忘在我家<delay8 />
就回去了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay8 />
我有其他事得處理，<delay8 />
沒辦法拿去還啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<tag a="110" b="3" />。<delay8 />
不好意思啊，<delay8 />能不能麻煩你<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />代替我去<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那跑一趟啊？</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你自己去吧</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子啊，<delay8 />
原本要寄給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的包裹，<delay8 />
跑到了我這來。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我現在有點忙，<delay8 />
沒時間<delay8 />送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但繼續放在我這也不好<tag a="110" b="0" />
這下該怎麼辦啊？</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我幫你送過去</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後再去吧</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啊，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />
那就交給你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />
那這東西就交給你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意幫我送去啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你真是幫了大忙啊！<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那這個就拜託你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說的也是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
你說的對，<delay8 />
這種時候，還是只能老實道歉啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想也是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
拜託你把別人忘在我家的東西<delay8 />送回去，<delay8 />
這件事挺不合理的啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉拜託你這麼奇怪的事。<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己把這東西送回去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法了。<delay8 />
雖然這麼做很過意不去，<delay8 />
