就立刻送過去！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay8 />那個，
我有件事想跟你商量，<delay8 />
你能聽我說嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實啊<tag a="110" b="0" />我有個東西
想交給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是，<delay8 />我準備了禮物，想感謝<gender3 m="他" f="她" />平時的照顧。<delay8 />
但真要拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />的時候，<delay20 />
又覺得<delay8 />挺害臊的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我幫你送過去！</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
你能聽我說一下嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實，<delay8 />我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />
吵了一架<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />是我不好，<delay8 />我很幼稚地對<gender3 m="他" f="她" />發火。<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />後來覺得很尷尬，
一直沒向<gender3 m="他" f="她" />道歉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我想<delay8 />至少該送個賠罪的禮物，<delay8 />
