	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔，<delay8 />可以嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />謝啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />。
