<tag a="110" b="3" />！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />
聽你這麼一說，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好像就有勇氣啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝啦，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
